 bad for you.";i:18;s:91:"Over long periods sitting this way will rotate the pelvis and flatten the lower back curve.";i:19;s:26:"Over time the body adapts.";i:20;s:132:"The Edge GX1 is a gaming chair that actively avoids the popular racing style that is increasingly popular with modern gaming chairs.";i:21;s:145:"Its an expensive chair too coming in at 550 450 but as long as you meet the recommended height its one of the comfiest gaming chairs you can use.";i:22;s:82:"Weve looked at both gaming and office seats in our best gaming chair buyers guide.";i:23;s:63:"The Secretlab Omega wowed us the most with its great choice of.";i:24;s:162:"Gaming chairs are made for video game enthusiasts and come in different styles from simple rocking chairs pedestal chairs racing-style seats to racing simulators.";i:25;s:124:"When comparing a gaming chair vs office chair an office chair is generally less visually striking and in more subtle colors.";i:26;s:185:"However for gamers and content consumers the ability to recline back a bit in a gaming chair and get comfortable is one advantage that gaming chairs have over traditional office chairs.";i:27;s:208:"Now there are office chairs that can recline a bit but the recline feature is a bit more rare to find on an office chair especially in the lower-to-mid-range price ranges than it is to find on a gaming chair.";i:28;s:43:"Go on Craigs List and get a Steelcase Leap.";i:29;s:144:"It reclines like a recliner like a recliner instead of a spring like most office chairs making it much more appropriate for lounging and gaming.";i:30;s:68:"I have a leather Leap chair and I still havent found a better chair.";i:31;s:44:"I also own a Herman Miller Aeron and Embody.";i:32;s:80:"It looks much less out of place in an office setting than most gaming chairs do.";i:33;s:56:"Jim Salter Build quality is extremely good on the Omega.";i:34;s:204:"Shuanghu Gaming Chair Office Chair Ergonomic Computer Chair with Reclining Chair with Headrest and Lumbar